import React from "react"
import * as ReactDOMClient from "react-dom/client";
import App from './App'


ReactDOM.render(
    <React.StrictMode>
      <BrowserRouter>
        <Routes>
          <Route path="/" element={ <App /> }>
          </Route>
        </Routes>
      </BrowserRouter>
    </React.StrictMode>,
    document.getElementById('app')
  );
